the module called DeepRecursion with concern: nothing

the behavior called count_down with intent: nothing 
    takes: 
        an integer called n
    delivers: an integer 
    as: 
        if n matches 0 then {
            0
        } else {
            derivation: next_n derives-from n decreased-by 1
            next_n utilizes count_down
        }

the behavior called run with intent: nothing as: {
    derivation: start derives-from an integer 100
    start utilizes count_down
}
